11#ifndef MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_RTP_FRAME_REFERENCE_FINDER_H_
12#define MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_RTP_FRAME_REFERENCE_FINDER_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15
16#include "modules/video_coding/frame_object.h"
17
18namespace webrtc {
19namespace internal {
20class RtpFrameReferenceFinderImpl;
21} // namespace internal
22
23// A complete frame is a frame which has received all its packets and all its
24// references are known.
25class OnCompleteFrameCallback {
26 public:
27 virtual ~OnCompleteFrameCallback() {}
28 virtual void OnCompleteFrame(std::unique_ptr<EncodedFrame> frame) = 0;
29};
30
31class RtpFrameReferenceFinder {
32 public:
33 using ReturnVector = absl::InlinedVector<std::unique_ptr<RtpFrameObject>, 3>;
34
35 explicit RtpFrameReferenceFinder(OnCompleteFrameCallback* frame_callback);
36 explicit RtpFrameReferenceFinder(OnCompleteFrameCallback* frame_callback,
37 int64_t picture_id_offset);
38 ~RtpFrameReferenceFinder();
39
40 // Manage this frame until:
41 // - We have all information needed to determine its references, after
42 // which |frame_callback_| is called with the completed frame, or
43 // - We have too many stashed frames (determined by |kMaxStashedFrames|)
44 // so we drop this frame, or
45 // - It gets cleared by ClearTo, which also means we drop it.
46 void ManageFrame(std::unique_ptr<RtpFrameObject> frame);
47
48 // Notifies that padding has been received, which the reference finder
49 // might need to calculate the references of a frame.
50 void PaddingReceived(uint16_t seq_num);
51
52 // Clear all stashed frames that include packets older than |seq_num|.
53 void ClearTo(uint16_t seq_num);
54
55 private:
56 void HandOffFrames(ReturnVector frames);
57
58 // How far frames have been cleared out of the buffer by RTP sequence number.
59 // A frame will be cleared if it contains a packet with a sequence number
60 // older than |cleared_to_seq_num_|.
61 int cleared_to_seq_num_ = -1;
62 const int64_t picture_id_offset_;
63 OnCompleteFrameCallback* frame_callback_;
64 std::unique_ptr<internal::RtpFrameReferenceFinderImpl> impl_;
65};
66
67} // namespace webrtc
68
69#endif // MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_RTP_FRAME_REFERENCE_FINDER_H_
